  "content_markdown": "Alongside this PS, the PRA has re-launched the [New Banks Start-up Unit webpage](https://www.bankofengland.co.uk/prudential-regulation/new-bank-start-up-unit). The updated webpage has been developed as a reference tool for firms considering setting up a bank in the UK, and for newly authorised firms, and contains information covering a range of supervisory topics. We encourage firms to use this as a key source of information when developing their business propositions and regulatory documents.\n",
